Version: 0.1.23
Date: 2026-04-14

Changes:
- WeChat workflow polish:
  - REPL `:wechat` / `/wechat` command keeps login + listen behavior in sync with WeChat mode usage.
  - WeChat output defaults to final-reply-only mode; turn-by-turn progress remains opt-in.
  - transport reliability hardening remains in place for poll/send edge cases.
- Tool guidance tuning:
  - improve `write_file` description to emphasize full overwrite intent.
  - improve `edit_file` description to encourage targeted edits over full rewrites.
- Stability:
  - harden a flaky filesystem integration test path (`tools_fs_pack`) to reduce intermittent publish-time failures.
- Docs:
  - refresh README wording around WeChat usage and progress behavior.

Related commits:
- chore(release): bundle latest workspace changes and publish patch
